name: Bristles - Rain Forest Lantern
description:
The floors of Tasmania rain forests contain a wealth of diverse flora (and leeches). This toadstool’s bright orange hue gives the appearance of a faerie streetlight to the drab browns and greens of the surrounding foliage.

Original photography filtered through the lens of generative abstraction. Digital oil painted onto a noisy geometric canvas. 6000x6000. Made in Processing.
